thread.title: Eurogroup ministers to meet this week to discuss Greek vote - spokesman
thread.title_full: Eurogroup ministers to meet this week to discuss Greek vote - spokesman | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Eurogroup ministers to meet this week to discuss Greek vote - spokesman
text:
AMSTERDAM, July 5 The finance ministers of the Eurogroup will meet this week to discuss the outcome of the Greek referendum, a spokesman for group chairman Jeroen Dijsselbloem said on Sunday.
The ministers are not expected to meet on Monday, but later in the week, said Michel Reijns. (Reporting By Anthony Deutsch; Editing by Kevin Liffey )
